                        <p>The DeepLearner Platform (TDP), was a platform dedicated to teaching our peers at Iowa State University machine learning topics. 
                            Built on the AWS DeepRacer car, TDP implemented the training environment for autonomous car driving models locally, on our school servers rather than using AWS saving funds for our proejct. 
